00:08:20.996 --> 00:08:23.370 align:middle line:84%
So I'm not judging our past
as right, wrong, good or bad.

00:08:23.370 --> 00:08:25.140 align:middle line:90%
We're in a huge learning curve.

00:08:25.140 --> 00:08:26.510 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And it's brought
a lot of awareness about--

00:08:26.510 --> 00:08:28.926 align:middle line:84%
>>BRADEN: It has brought a
