00:08:28.926 --> 00:08:30.010 align:middle line:90%
So the changes.

00:08:30.010 --> 00:08:33.120 align:middle line:84%
Now, this is where the
science and our most cherished

00:08:33.120 --> 00:08:35.130 align:middle line:84%
