00:08:36.390 --> 00:08:40.330 align:middle line:84%
Because the science is telling
us about cycles of time

00:08:40.330 --> 00:08:42.039 align:middle line:90%
that are bringing the changes.

00:08:42.039 --> 00:08:44.375 align:middle line:84%
But they've only recently
begun to understand those.

00:08:44.375 --> 00:08:46.250 align:middle line:84%
Our indigenous ancestors
have been telling us

00:08:46.250 --> 00:08:49.550 align:middle line:84%
for 5,000 years,
look out, generation

00:08:49.550 --> 00:08:52.580 align:middle line:84%
of the early 20th century,
right around the year 2012.

00:08:52.580 --> 00:08:54.120 align:middle line:90%
It's not the end of the world.

00:08:54.120 --> 00:08:57.360 align:middle line:84%
It's the end of a cycle of
time called a Great World Age.

00:08:57.360 --> 00:09:00.719 align:middle line:84%
And with that, you can expect
some big changes in your life.

00:09:00.719 --> 00:09:02.510 align:middle line:84%
And so this is what
I'd like to talk about.

00:09:02.510 --> 00:09:03.266 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Absolutely

00:09:03.266 --> 00:09:04.640 align:middle line:84%
>>BRADEN: Right
now, the changes.

00:09:04.640 --> 00:09:06.700 align:middle line:84%
People are asking,
what's different?

00:09:06.700 --> 00:09:08.010 align:middle line:90%
What causes the changes?

00:09:08.010 --> 00:09:10.980 align:middle line:84%
They're triggered by
Earth's location in space.

00:09:10.980 --> 00:09:13.060 align:middle line:90%
Earth is a very dynamic system.

00:09:13.060 --> 00:09:15.260 align:middle line:84%
We all know that it spins
to create night and day

00:09:15.260 --> 00:09:17.130 align:middle line:90%
and tilts for the seasons.

00:09:17.130 --> 00:09:18.310 align:middle line:90%
It does much more than that.

00:09:18.310 --> 00:09:20.510 align:middle line:84%
In space, it's the orbit,
the tilt, the angle,

00:09:20.510 --> 00:09:23.890 align:middle line:84%
the wobble of Earth
in space, and how

00:09:23.890 --> 00:09:26.520 align:middle line:84%
it changes our relationship
to the sun, the energy

00:09:26.520 --> 00:09:29.040 align:middle line:84%
that we receive from the sun,
from the center of our Milky

00:09:29.040 --> 00:09:30.200 align:middle line:90%
Way galaxy.

00:09:30.200 --> 00:09:32.980 align:middle line:84%
Now, our own science
through the ice cores

00:09:32.980 --> 00:09:36.110 align:middle line:84%
in Antarctica and the poles
have begun to confirm this.

00:09:36.110 --> 00:09:39.249 align:middle line:84%
And we're going to talk
about this in more detail.

00:09:39.249 --> 00:09:40.790 align:middle line:84%
Our own science now
is confirming it.

00:09:40.790 --> 00:09:42.890 align:middle line:84%
But our indigenous
ancestors knew this.

00:09:42.890 --> 00:09:46.136 align:middle line:84%
Somehow they knew this
without ice cores, and GPS,

00:09:46.136 --> 00:09:47.385 align:middle line:90%
and computers, and satellites.

00:09:47.385 --> 00:09:49.880 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Well, they've been
