00:09:52.018 --> 00:09:54.170 align:middle line:84%
And they knew because they
understood the cycles.

00:09:54.170 --> 00:09:57.750 align:middle line:84%
And this is one of the things
that Western traditions

00:09:57.750 --> 00:09:59.530 align:middle line:90%
