00:09:59.530 --> 00:10:03.400 align:middle line:84%
We have been led to think of
ourselves in a linear fashion.

00:10:03.400 --> 00:10:05.320 align:middle line:84%
That civilization
happened the one time

00:10:05.320 --> 00:10:09.660 align:middle line:84%
