where we are today.

00:10:09.660 --> 00:10:11.010 align:middle line:90%
In very linear terms.

00:10:11.010 --> 00:10:13.420 align:middle line:84%
The rest of the world, in
the ancient traditions,

00:10:13.420 --> 00:10:15.920 align:middle line:84%
have traditionally thought of
our lives and our relationship

00:10:15.920 --> 00:10:17.253 align:middle line:90%
to the world in terms of cycles.

00:10:17.253 --> 00:10:19.080 align:middle line:84%
So the cycle that
we're living now.

00:10:19.080 --> 00:10:20.800 align:middle line:84%
They say, of course
the world's going

00:10:20.800 --> 00:10:22.350 align:middle line:84%
