end of a way of life.

00:10:28.619 --> 00:10:29.660 align:middle line:90%
Not the end of the world.

00:10:29.660 --> 00:10:31.910 align:middle line:84%
The end of a way of life
that's no longer sustainable.

00:10:31.910 --> 00:10:33.840 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That's no
longer working, yes.

00:10:33.840 --> 00:10:35.590 align:middle line:84%
>>BRADEN: It's like a
great reality check.

00:10:35.590 --> 00:10:37.401 align:middle line:90%
A cosmic reality check.

00:10:37.401 --> 00:10:39.150 align:middle line:84%
We get to see what
