We're all affected by it
because we're losing our houses.

00:27:52.400 --> 00:27:55.660 align:middle line:84%
We're never going to see the
housing market the way it was.

00:27:55.660 --> 00:27:59.200 align:middle line:84%
It's definitely affecting
every single person

00:27:59.200 --> 00:28:01.260 align:middle line:84%
at the survivalistic
level, which

00:28:01.260 --> 00:28:03.874 align:middle line:84%
is why this information is so
important to consume right now.

00:28:03.874 --> 00:28:04.540 align:middle line:90%
>>BRADEN: It is.

00:28:04.540 --> 00:28:07.610 align:middle line:84%
The way we have thought
about ourselves in the past

00:28:07.610 --> 00:28:09.480 align:middle line:84%
is changing so
very, very quickly.

00:28:09.480 --> 00:28:12.090 align:middle line:84%
So it's obvious we are
living a time of extremes.

00:28:12.090 --> 00:28:13.780 align:middle line:84%
And we're being
told we must act.

00:28:13.780 --> 00:28:15.581 align:middle line:90%
My question is this-- how?

00:28:15.581 --> 00:28:16.080 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: How.

00:28:16.080 --> 00:28:16.890 align:middle line:90%
>>BRADEN: How.

00:28:16.890 --> 00:28:20.170 align:middle line:84%
How are we supposed to act
so differently so quickly?

00:28:20.170 --> 00:28:21.880 align:middle line:84%
What we're really
asking is this--

00:28:21.880 --> 00:28:24.650 align:middle line:84%
how can we possibly
make the greatest

00:28:24.650 --> 00:28:28.490 align:middle line:84%
choices of our survival until
we understand the deepest

00:28:28.490 --> 00:28:31.080 align:middle line:90%
truths of our existence?

00:28:31.080 --> 00:28:34.900 align:middle line:84%
How can we make the
greatest choices of survival

00:28:34.900 --> 00:28:38.180 align:middle line:84%
until we understand the deepest
truths of our existence?

00:28:38.180 --> 00:28:41.350 align:middle line:84%
And many of those truths are
based upon false assumptions

00:28:41.350 --> 00:28:43.220 align:middle line:84%
of science that have
been perpetuated

00:28:43.220 --> 00:28:45.315 align:middle line:84%
for over a century, almost
a century and a half.

00:28:45.315 --> 00:28:47.690 align:middle line:84%
And this is where we're going
with all of this right now.

00:28:47.690 --> 00:28:48.990 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: This is perfect timing.

00:28:48.990 --> 00:28:52.354 align:middle line:90%
And keep going.

00:28:52.354 --> 00:28:54.270 align:middle line:84%
>>BRADEN: It all comes
down to a very simple--

00:28:54.270 --> 00:28:55.619 align:middle line:90%
deceptively simple question.

00:28:55.619 --> 00:28:57.160 align:middle line:84%
And the question on
your screen right

00:28:57.160 --> 00:28:59.646 align:middle line:90%
