00:28:59.646 --> 00:29:01.020 align:middle line:84%
Or there are many
of us together.

00:29:01.020 --> 00:29:02.494 align:middle line:90%
Who are we?

00:29:02.494 --> 00:29:03.910 align:middle line:84%
And the reason
this is important--

00:29:03.910 --> 00:29:05.570 align:middle line:84%
people say, what
does that have to do

00:29:05.570 --> 00:29:07.330 align:middle line:90%
