I'm going to invite
you to consider

00:29:10.430 --> 00:29:13.130 align:middle line:84%
that every challenge that's
ever crossed your path,

00:29:13.130 --> 00:29:15.270 align:middle line:84%
every problem that
you've ever had to solve,

00:29:15.270 --> 00:29:19.380 align:middle line:84%
every crisis that you ever
will or have experienced

00:29:19.380 --> 00:29:22.640 align:middle line:84%
in the past, the way you have
dealt with all of these things

00:29:22.640 --> 00:29:24.270 align:middle line:84%
all filters through
the lens of the way

00:29:24.270 --> 00:29:27.950 align:middle line:84%
you answer this simple question,
who are you or who are we.

00:29:27.950 --> 00:29:30.700 align:middle line:84%
Because the way we think of
ourselves, and our relationship

00:29:30.700 --> 00:29:33.000 align:middle line:84%
to this Earth, to our
bodies, and one another

00:29:33.000 --> 00:29:36.020 align:middle line:84%
is the filter through which
we will choose our answers

00:29:36.020 --> 00:29:37.980 align:middle line:90%
and create our solutions.

00:29:37.980 --> 00:29:38.580 align:middle line:90%
Precisely.

00:29:38.580 --> 00:29:39.330 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And that
, I will assert,

00:29:39.330 --> 00:29:41.300 align:middle line:84%
is going into the future
with your purpose,

00:29:41.300 --> 00:29:43.900 align:middle line:84%
with what you want to achieve
in your life, what you--

00:29:43.900 --> 00:29:46.515 align:middle line:84%
your goals, has everything to
do with how you answer this

00:29:46.515 --> 00:29:46.600 align:middle line:90%
question.

00:29:46.600 --> 00:29:47.420 align:middle line:84%
>>BRADEN: That's what this
whole series is about.

00:29:47.420 --> 00:29:49.350 align:middle line:84%
You are going to
have many guests--

00:29:49.350 --> 00:29:51.310 align:middle line:84%
you've had in the past,
and after I'm finished,

00:29:51.310 --> 00:29:54.560 align:middle line:84%
you'll have in the future--
