of weapons, mass graves,

00:59:18.100 --> 00:59:18.970 align:middle line:90%
mutilated bodies.

00:59:18.970 --> 00:59:22.810 align:middle line:84%
We see no evidence of that,
no walls around the cities,

00:59:22.810 --> 00:59:25.420 align:middle line:84%
no moats protecting the
cities, no evidence of weapons

00:59:25.420 --> 00:59:27.270 align:middle line:90%
