civilization in that time.

00:59:31.350 --> 00:59:31.790 align:middle line:90%
Scientific evidence.

00:59:31.790 --> 00:59:32.915 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That's fascinating.

00:59:32.915 --> 00:59:38.190 align:middle line:84%
So war, it did not exist back
in-- prior to the 5,125-year

00:59:38.190 --> 00:59:39.190 align:middle line:90%
cycle that we're ending.

00:59:39.190 --> 00:59:40.060 align:middle line:84%
>>BRADEN: One of two
things is happening.

