war, defending--

00:59:51.750 --> 00:59:53.490 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: The need for defense.

00:59:53.490 --> 00:59:54.770 align:middle line:90%
>>BRADEN: --huge armies.

00:59:54.770 --> 00:59:58.190 align:middle line:84%
Solving their problems with
a neighboring community

00:59:58.190 --> 01:00:00.350 align:middle line:84%
with huge armies
destroying one another,

01:00:00.350 --> 01:00:03.030 align:middle line:84%
