01:00:05.590 --> 01:00:06.298 align:middle line:90%
>>BRADEN: We are.

01:00:06.298 --> 01:00:08.820 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: --that are
currently even going

01:00:08.820 --> 01:00:11.390 align:middle line:90%
under archaeological digs.

01:00:11.390 --> 01:00:12.320 align:middle line:90%
>>BRADEN: Absolutely.

01:00:12.320 --> 01:00:15.400 align:middle line:84%
So what we know now is nature
is based on cooperation, not

01:00:15.400 --> 01:00:16.050 align:middle line:90%
competition.

01:00:16.050 --> 01:00:18.680 align:middle line:84%
It's actually based on
what is called mutual aid

01:00:18.680 --> 01:00:20.640 align:middle line:84%
and cooperation,
not competition.

01:00:20.640 --> 01:00:22.815 align:middle line:84%
And I may not be doing
justice to the topic

01:00:22.815 --> 01:00:24.940 align:middle line:84%
