01:00:27.661 --> 01:00:28.880 align:middle line:90%
This isn't a workshop.

01:00:28.880 --> 01:00:30.170 align:middle line:90%
This is--

01:00:30.170 --> 01:00:32.600 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I'm also very
curious because what Darwin

01:00:32.600 --> 01:00:34.320 align:middle line:84%
