these false assumptions.

01:00:57.020 --> 01:00:58.720 align:middle line:84%
The second one is
that civilization

01:00:58.720 --> 01:01:00.750 align:middle line:84%
itself began about
5,000 years ago.

01:01:00.750 --> 01:01:03.720 align:middle line:84%
And people say, what's
the big deal about that?

01:01:03.720 --> 01:01:06.610 align:middle line:84%
Whether it began a million years
or 5,000 years, why do we care?

01:01:06.610 --> 01:01:09.500 align:middle line:84%
And it's important
because of the cycles.

01:01:09.500 --> 01:01:12.450 align:middle line:84%
If we are living this rare
pivotal moment in the cycle

01:01:12.450 --> 01:01:15.219 align:middle line:84%
now, and civilizations
and humans like you

01:01:15.219 --> 01:01:17.010 align:middle line:84%
and me have lived
through this in the past,

01:01:17.010 --> 01:01:18.460 align:middle line:90%
