01:01:18.460 --> 01:01:20.850 align:middle line:84%
And it may give us
some insights into how

01:01:20.850 --> 01:01:23.260 align:middle line:84%
to deal with these crises
because they're rare.

01:01:23.260 --> 01:01:25.470 align:middle line:84%
We won't see this for
another 5,000 years,

01:01:25.470 --> 01:01:27.416 align:middle line:84%
