01:02:11.790 --> 01:02:13.840 align:middle line:84%
Because there's
something about us

01:02:13.840 --> 01:02:16.130 align:middle line:84%
that's really drawn
to the ancient, Lisa.

01:02:16.130 --> 01:02:18.320 align:middle line:84%
There's a sense,
