01:02:32.780 --> 01:02:34.710 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: This is exciting.

01:02:34.710 --> 01:02:36.550 align:middle line:90%
>>BRADEN: So 5,500 years.

01:02:36.550 --> 01:02:39.620 align:middle line:84%
I personally have had the
opportunity to document.

01:02:39.620 --> 01:02:42.720 align:middle line:84%
In northern Peru
right now, there's

01:02:42.720 --> 01:02:45.100 align:middle line:84%
an ongoing archaeological
site 150 acres,

01:02:45.100 --> 01:02:47.360 align:middle line:84%
