two things would happen.

01:04:25.620 --> 01:04:29.160 align:middle line:84%
Either this would become
just another Incan site--

01:04:29.160 --> 01:04:31.556 align:middle line:84%
a very cool Incan site--
dated with everything else.

01:04:31.556 --> 01:04:33.680 align:middle line:84%
Or it would be the oldest
site in all the Americas.

01:04:33.680 --> 01:04:35.670 align:middle line:84%
And I saw he turned
his back to me.

01:04:35.670 --> 01:04:38.275 align:middle line:84%
And as he turned back around,
he had a huge smile on his face

01:04:38.275 --> 01:04:40.020 align:middle line:84%
