answer would be.

01:04:40.020 --> 01:04:41.950 align:middle line:84%
That was the day we
discovered that this

01:04:41.950 --> 01:04:46.080 align:middle line:84%
was dated between 5,000
years and 7,000 years BP,

01:04:46.080 --> 01:04:47.660 align:middle line:90%
Before Present.

01:04:47.660 --> 01:04:49.830 align:middle line:84%
Older than any of
these sites should be.

01:04:49.830 --> 01:04:50.830 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: What did you do?

01:04:50.830 --> 01:04:52.020 align:middle line:90%
Did you sit down?

01:04:52.020 --> 01:04:55.687 align:middle line:84%
What did you do when you
found that information?

01:04:55.687 --> 01:04:56.770 align:middle line:90%
>>BRADEN: In all honesty--

01:04:56.770 --> 01:04:56.790 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Do you remember?

01:04:56.790 --> 01:04:57.440 align:middle line:90%
>>BRADEN: --I wasn't surprised.

01:04:57.440 --> 01:04:58.200 align:middle line:90%
I had a sense.

01:04:58.200 --> 01:05:00.580 align:middle line:84%
